  "assumptions": [
    "Railway monolith deploy: API and BullMQ workers run in the same Node process for simplicity. Worker extraction to a separate Railway service is straightforward if needed.",
    "Redis is provisioned via Railway Redis plugin. Standard TCP Redis (not Upstash REST) — this is correct for Railway (not Cloudflare Workers).",
    "PostgreSQL is provisioned via Railway PostgreSQL plugin. DATABASE_URL is injected automatically.",
